item.title: CVE-2015-8988|2024-08-06T08:36:31.576Z -- intel -- epo%20deep%20command%20%28edc%29
item.description: Unquoted executable path vulnerability in Client Management and Gateway components in McAfee (now Intel Security) ePO Deep Command (eDC) 2.2 and 2.1 allows authenticated users to execute a command of their choice via dropping a malicious file for the path.
